data.description: Stunning 5 bedroom Taylor Morrison home on 1 acre w/ a fruit trees! Upon entering through your covered front porch, you'll find a dedicated office space, featuring French doors for privacy. 10ft ceilings on main. Open floor plan. Dining area is open to your spacious + light filled living room (w/ tray ceilings) as well as your gorgeous chefs kitchen + breakfast area. The heart of your home will surely be the kitchen with a massive eat-at island, ss appliances, beautiful cabinetry, pantry + gas stove. Out back is the large screened in back patio that overlooks a fenced backyard w/ new 700sqft stone patio. Primary oasis includes bay windows, tray ceilings + stunning en-suite w/ oversize stand alone shower w/ walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms are all sizable and share full bathrooms. Upstairs, you will find two large bedrooms + a full bathroom. Seller is willing to increase price to offer closing costs to buy down your rate which will lower your monthly payment.
